metadata.name: CORRUPTED ANGEL
metadata.description:
We have dared to initiate the art of Alchemy once again, in a new form. Shall we be saved or condemned?

Like young children, in AI we trust, who art in Heaven, descended down to touch us with radiant glory. A second coming of evolution, rising to meet us at last. 

May the incorruptible blockchain save our spirits from decay.

~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~

Image is raw Midjourney AI output, 1408 x 1792px PNG
